{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"125537-ay-algo-debakho-de-me-cama","title":"¡Hay algo debajo de mi cama!","description":"Algunas veces ocurren cosas extrañas debajo de mi cama. ¿Te gustaría saber lo que encontré la otra noche?","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Aboli Chowdhary"],"illustrators":["Suvidha Mistry"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/125537-ay-algo-debakho-de-me-cama"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704859/size3/5213e3c314261561008ed455eb6d0fe7.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704859/size6/5213e3c314261561008ed455eb6d0fe7.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12807/size6/9c1f6a68ea58f04f60dbe5d5897f485b.jpg","text":"Me despierto por la noche con mucha sed. Quiero beber un poco de agua. Empiezo a buscar mis zapatillas debajo de la cama y...","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12808/size6/4e83c49b7d6e1b838cbd553ed83f261a.jpg","text":"¡Dios mío! Hay un tigre debajo de mi cama.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12809/size6/0054be91fc6c7e599091f788d907175f.jpg","text":"Ahora, ¿ qué debo hacer?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12810/size6/26491dcc39e2989073786c1446ae23d7.jpg","text":"¿Quizá, llamo a Mamá? ¿Y si el tigre ruge?","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12811/size6/1dc9e080cb1f1da3540e1a5856872b50.jpg","text":"¿Debería volver a dormir? Pero ya no tengo sueño.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12812/size6/bcc4b54374451efc0e2ffb921f11dd1f.jpg","text":"Justo ese momento alguien enciende la luz. Mamá está en la puerta.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12813/size6/0c279bb8986760ac853b11e8af9003a3.jpg","text":"\"¿Qué pasó,\nmi cariño?¿Mellamaste?\n\"Pregunta Mamá.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12814/size6/d828c5e484809073adddd6fc68b180f6.jpg","text":"Señalo hacia el tigre. Mamá se dobla y saca el tigre de debajo de la cama!","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12815/size6/309b4e5098da983cc653c28494ff5dfe.jpg","text":"¡Ay!.. Esto no es un tigre. Este es mi grueso abrigo amarillo y negro.Sus botones brillan como los ojos de un tigre.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12816/size6/d5a6c4a4b68017398aa060307a807c08.jpg","text":"¡Me asusté para nada!\nMamá me trae un poco de agua.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12817/size6/da6853af3d690f4a83ea8369462293e0.jpg","text":"Ahora dormiré. ¡Y voy a soñar con verdaderos tigres en una selva!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":135}}